                                    <li class="list-group-item"><strong>Zip Wire</strong> – Adrenaline junkie or willing to face a fear? There’s zip wires up and down the country and all offer a different experience. So do your research and find the challenge that is right for you (and most likely to encourage friends to sponsor you).</li>
